WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.440 --> 00:00:05.520
It's as if you've worked a long day in your life, you've worked a long day and then

2
00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:10.720
you come home, you can take off your shoes, you

3
00:00:10.720 --> 00:00:15.860
can sit in your armchair with a good beer,

4
00:00:15.960 --> 00:00:21.120
it's a stage for you, where you are happy

5
00:00:21.120 --> 00:00:26.300
with the work you've done, for once you're happy, you say to yourself, "There, a big job

6
00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:26.860
has been done."

7
00:00:28.058 --> 00:00:33.138
You're sitting there, you're resting a little, you're resting your body a little,

8
00:00:33.318 --> 00:00:36.118
and then you rest your mind a little.

9
00:00:41.058 --> 00:00:43.518
You develop a small quality in your mind.

10
00:00:44.198 --> 00:00:47.238
You light this small flame that I'm going to suggest you light,

11
00:00:47.538 --> 00:00:53.018
which is a small flame that should try to remind you of contentment.

12
00:00:53.018 --> 00:00:55.798
To learn to...

13
00:00:56.116 --> 00:00:58.196
instant, to appreciate what we have.

14
00:01:05.836 --> 00:01:07.896
We're off to the skull.